    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Paperlands》是一款 2D 益智冒险游戏，背景为纸艺世界。在这个世界中，只有通过色彩赋予生命的事物才能进行互动。一个孩子曾开始为这个世界上色，但很快就被分散了注意力，导致世界未能完成。帮助 Paperlands 的居民完成未竟的任务，让 Paperlands 重新焕发生机！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为物体和人物上色，才能与它们互动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196370/extras/b30a2909edb0db2a111abe338940b7f4.poster.avif?t=1771049594\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196370/extras/b30a2909edb0db2a111abe338940b7f4.webm?t=1771049594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196370/extras/b30a2909edb0db2a111abe338940b7f4.mp4?t=1771049594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解开谜题，解锁新颜色，并到达新地点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196370/extras/a5ebe87f436513b9ea6b81305fce0862.poster.avif?t=1771049594\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196370/extras/a5ebe87f436513b9ea6b81305fce0862.webm?t=1771049594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196370/extras/a5ebe87f436513b9ea6b81305fce0862.mp4?t=1771049594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发挥创意，按照你的喜好为世界上色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196370/extras/605e83c7e5d5e016a0c74ecb0e551ce4.poster.avif?t=1771049594\" width=800 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196370/extras/605e83c7e5d5e016a0c74ecb0e551ce4.webm?t=1771049594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196370/extras/605e83c7e5d5e016a0c74ecb0e551ce4.mp4?t=1771049594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅途中帮助 Paperlands 的居民。</p></li></ul>",
